title: Lisa Gardner Detective D D Warren series 2007-2014
description:
Number one New York Times bestselling author Lisa Gardner thrills readers with her novels of suspense featuring Boston homicide detective D. D. Warren. Hostage standoffs, copycat killers, missing wives, brutal crimes, haunted survivors

Detective D.D. Warren series
    Hide (2007), 
    The Neighbor (2009), 
    Live to Tell (2010), 
    Love You More (2011), 
    Catch Me (2012), 
    The 7th Month (2012)
    Fear Nothing (2014)
